  "attachmentHtml": "\n<p><strong>PC Number: </strong>2019-0974<br></p><p><strong>Date: </strong>2019-06-27</p><hr><p>\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nHer Excellency the Governor General in Council, on&nbsp;the&nbsp;recommendation of the Minister of the Environment, makes&nbsp;the annexed <em>Output-Based Pricing System Regulations</em> pursuant to\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(a) sections 192, 193, 198 and 256 of the <em>Greenhouse Gas&nbsp;Pollution Pricing Act</em>; and\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(b) section 5 of the <em>Environmental Violations Administrative&nbsp;Monetary Penalties Act</em>.\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nSur recommandation de la ministre de l’Environnement, Son Excellence la Gouverneure générale en conseil prend le <em>Règlement sur le système de tarification fondé sur le rendement</em>, ci-après&nbsp;:\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\na) en vertu des articles 192, 193, 198 et 256 de la&nbsp;<em>Loi&nbsp;sur&nbsp;la&nbsp;tarification de la pollution causée par les&nbsp;gaz&nbsp;à effet&nbsp;de&nbsp;serre</em>;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nb) en vertu de l’article 5 de la <em>Loi sur les pénalités administratives en matière d’environnement</em>.</p>\n\n<p></p><form method=\"post\" action=\"index.php\"><input type=\"submit\" value=\"Back to Form\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" name=\"return\"></form>\t\t\n        <!-- end main content -->\n        <div id=\"def-preFooter\">\n       \t\t<!-- Write closure fall-back static file -->\n             <!--Response.Write readFile(\"StaticFallbackFiles/gcweb/preFooter-\" & $lang & \".html\") -->\n        </div>\n\t\t<!-- Write closure template -->\n        <script type=\"text/javascript\">\n            var defPreFooter = document.getElementById(\"def-preFooter\");\n            defPreFooter.outerHTML = wet.builder.preFooter({\n                cdnEnv: \"prod\",\n                dateModified: \"2022-07-11\",\n                showPostContent: true\n            });\n        </script>\n    "
